# THIS IS ABOUT CSS DESIGN

* css is stands for (cascading style sheet) and we use it in our website to design the content
of the webpage and decorate it 
content structure to users interface structure and there is three ways to styling our website :
    - ### inline style it happens like this :
         <p style :"color:rgb(50,60,120)">
    - ### internal style thats happend in the head :
         **<style>body{propaerty:value;}</style>**
    - ### external style sheet thats done in separate file of CSS and compare it by link .
    
#### the best practic to doing the CSS is the external style cheet cause it :
    
   - more effecient to seo (searchnengine optimization )and its most comfortable when you contact with 
    too many html file and css file for each of them .
   - will enhance the performance on web browser and the seo issues . 
